"title": "5341: hunger",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5341",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A state of emptiness, reflecting a lack of physical or spiritual food. Scripture recognises the physical aspects of human hunger which can only be met by the living God.</p>\n<h2>Kinds of hunger</h2>\n<h3>Physical</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">DEU 8:3</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Spiritual</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:6\">MAT 5:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:1\">PSA 63:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:5\">PSA 63:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:9\">PSA 107:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:11\">AMO 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:21\">LUK 6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:35\">JHN 6:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:2\">1PE 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Causes of hunger</h2>\n<h3>Famine</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:55\">GEN 41:55</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:25-2Kgs6:29\">2KI 6:25–6:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:1-Neh5:2\">NEH 5:1–5:2</a></p>\n<h3>Fasting</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:2\">MAT 4:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:2\">LUK 4:2</a></p>\n<h3>Fatigue</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:3\">1SA 21:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:29\">2SA 17:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:1-Matt12:4\">MAT 12:1–12:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:35-Mark6:36\">MRK 6:35–6:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:2-Mark8:3\">MRK 8:2–8:3</a></p>\n<h3>Folly</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:15\">PRO 19:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:4\">PRO 20:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:14\">LUK 15:14</a></p>\n<h3>God's action</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:26\">LEV 26:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:48\">DEU 28:48</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:13\">ISA 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:20\">ISA 9:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:19\">EZK 7:19</a></p>\n<h3>The hardships of gospel work</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:11\">1CO 4:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:5\">2CO 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:27\">2CO 11:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:12\">PHP 4:12</a></p>\n<h2>Effects of hunger</h2>\n<h3>Physical deterioration</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:3\">JOB 30:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:19\">LAM 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:9\">LAM 4:9</a></p>\n<h3>Mental preoccupation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:8\">ISA 29:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:10-Acts10:13\">ACT 10:10–10:13</a> <em>Peter's consciousness was supernaturally heightened to receive a vision from God.</em></p>\n<h3>Moral degradation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:29\">LEV 26:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:53\">DEU 28:53</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:28-2Kgs6:29\">2KI 6:28–6:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:9\">JER 19:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:20\">LAM 2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:10\">LAM 4:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:10\">EZK 5:10</a></p>\n<h3>An occasion for temptation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:6\">GEN 3:6</a> <em>Eve</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:29-Gen25:34\">GEN 25:29–25:34</a> <em>Esau</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:30-Prov6:31\">PRO 6:30–6:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:21\">ISA 8:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:3\">MAT 4:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:3\">LUK 4:3</a> <em>Jesus Christ</em></p>\n<h3>An opportunity for proving God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">DEU 8:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:15\">NEH 9:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:12\">PHP 4:12</a></p>\n<h2>God satisfies hunger</h2>\n<h3>He provides food for all creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:9\">PSA 107:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:15-Ps145:16\">PSA 145:15–145:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:13-Deut32:14\">DEU 32:13–32:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:14\">PSA 17:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:25\">PSA 37:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:21\">PSA 104:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:27-Ps104:28\">PSA 104:27–104:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:5\">PSA 111:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:15\">PSA 132:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:25\">PSA 136:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:7\">PSA 146:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:9\">PSA 147:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:10\">ISA 49:10</a></p>\n<h3>He provides through supernatural means</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:24-Ps78:25\">PSA 78:24–78:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:12-Exod16:15\">EXO 16:12–16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:4-1Kgs17:16\">1KI 17:4–17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:15\">NEH 9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:19-Matt14:21\">MAT 14:19–14:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:41-Mark6:44\">MRK 6:41–6:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:16-Luke9:17\">LUK 9:16–9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:11-John6:14\">JHN 6:11–6:14</a> <em>the feeding of the 5,000</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:7-Mark8:8\">MRK 8:7–8:8</a></p>\n<h3>He provides through natural means</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17-Gen3:19\">GEN 3:17–3:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:12\">JOS 5:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:26\">PRO 16:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:7\">ISA 58:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:35\">MAT 25:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:10\">2TH 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>He provides completely in heaven</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:16\">REV 7:16</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ was hungry</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:2\">MAT 4:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:2\">LUK 4:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:18\">MAT 21:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:12\">MRK 11:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:31\">JHN 4:31</a></p>",
